column5: I dont know much about moose but i do know i would not be that close to a couple of ticked off moose.
awesome, i'd love to witness something like that in person
Awesome clip thanks! The "tags" say Wyoming so most likely from there.
Awesome.  Being there, one wouldn't know whether to reach for T.P or their bow...
yipes, I wouldn't want to be that close to a couple of irate meese.
very cool and rare to see that.  but i agree i would not wantot be that close to the action.  nose bleeds seats for me would have been just fine.  CHeers!
That's Nutz!! Seen one of those thing up nort, thier freakin huge. And acutally that day as we were traveling threw muskoka an officer hit one and was killed.
